PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER No. 5 - which declares the severe flooding which started on February 28, 1992, in and around the Town of Peace River, Alberta, to be of concern to the federal government and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the Province of Alberta in respect thereof.
